Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.52,0:00:09.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, turn your sadness into kindness,\Nyour uniqueness into strength
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.85,0:00:17.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you get lost, let’s start walking
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.19,0:00:20.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One more time
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.19,0:00:26.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you really happy
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.98,0:00:30.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when you're always meeting\Nto someone's expectations?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.69,0:00:34.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you change to\Nwho you really wanna be
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.60,0:00:37.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you always have a great smile?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.90,0:00:45.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dreaming of only “the beginning,”\NI wake up
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.52,0:00:54.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and someday, I'll live on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.77,0:01:02.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, precious things are never in shape
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.94,0:01:09.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You never know what it is\Nwhen you get it or lose it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.89,0:01:17.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, turn your sadness into kindness,\Nyour uniqueness into strength
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.27,0:01:26.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you get lost,\Nlet's start walking
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.89,0:01:28.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One more time
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.56,0:01:47.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei!\NPlease stop this match right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.94,0:01:59.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There’s nothing to worry about…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.35,0:02:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.02,0:02:06.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sasuke and I…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.44,0:02:10.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We didn’t just get here late\Nfor no reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.69,0:02:25.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Late for the Show, But Ready to Go!\NThe Ultimate Secret Technique is Born!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.90,0:02:31.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The third eye…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.15,0:02:34.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no doubt… That Jutsu is…!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.27,0:02:37.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Darn…Gaara…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.44,0:02:42.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tora, Saru, Ne, Tatsu, Tori,\Nlnu, Ne…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.10,0:02:47.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mi, Inu, Uma, Ushi, Tora, U, Tori…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.02,0:02:52.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tatsu, Mi, Inu, Ne, Tora, Ushi, Saru…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.31,0:02:57.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tatsu, Mi, Hitsuji, Saru…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.89,0:02:59.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tori, Saru, I, Hitsuji, Uma…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.27,0:03:02.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tatsu, Tora…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.44,0:03:07.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tora, Saru, Ushi, Hitsuji, Ne, Uma…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.10,0:03:12.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tora, Ushi, Ne, Tora, Tatsu…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.44,0:03:15.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tori, Tatsu, Mi…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.10,0:03:20.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hitsuji, Saru, Tori…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.44,0:03:26.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tatsu, Tora, Hitsuji, Saru, Tori…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.98,0:03:28.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As I thought, it’s no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.56,0:03:32.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I, Hitsuji, Uma, Tatsu, Tatsu,\NTatsu, Ushi, Ne…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.73,0:03:36.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inu, I, Tori, Saru, Hitsuji, Uma…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.27,0:03:39.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Withdrawing like that…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.56,0:03:43.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t know what you’re up to…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.89,0:03:46.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but the timing is perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.60,0:03:51.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This thing of mine also takes time!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.31,0:04:18.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, is something the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.89,0:04:20.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.73,0:04:31.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It must be my imagination…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.89,0:04:33.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.98,0:04:56.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.89,0:04:57.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.48,0:05:01.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you mean when you said\Nthat you didn’t get here late for nothing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.89,0:05:04.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.44,0:05:06.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to know why?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.23,0:05:09.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said, this isn’t the time\Nto be talking about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.02,0:05:11.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up and watch him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.35,0:05:19.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‘Cause you’ll get a real surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.15,0:05:39.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That idiot…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.81,0:05:45.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gaara…we never know when\Nthe signal is going to come!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.15,0:05:50.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah…\NI’m gonna tear him open.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.94,0:05:54.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s how it comes out.\NWhat?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.65,0:05:57.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The contents…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.89,0:06:00.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lots and lots are coming out, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.19,0:06:04.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll give it all to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.90,0:06:08.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m always a good boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.02,0:06:11.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, let’s do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.44,0:06:15.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother, I’m watching so…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.19,0:06:22.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Darn! He’s totally useless,\Nno matter what we do now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.89,0:06:25.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He’s not even\Nabiding by the plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.27,0:06:27.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He looks like he’s just going\Nto screw things up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.40,0:06:28.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That Gaara!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.52,0:06:34.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey, wouldn’t it\Nbe better if we flee…?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.89,0:06:39.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Plan…?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.06,0:06:53.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How’s it going?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.89,0:06:56.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All preparations are proceeding\Nin accordance with the timeline.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.90,0:07:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please hurry up with preparation\Nfor Summoning.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.81,0:07:02.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to be sure we’re able to\Nmake our move at any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.48,0:07:04.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.98,0:07:07.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, I’ll leave that to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.60,0:07:46.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don’t tell me that…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.52,0:07:50.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The reason I decided to\Ntrain Sasuke was…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.23,0:07:55.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,because he was like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.27,0:08:13.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A physical Activation?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.89,0:08:15.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.02,0:08:18.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s why he went through\Nthe physical training
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.48,0:08:20.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and increased his speed significantly…!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.15,0:08:22.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.81,0:08:29.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Awesome…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.02,0:08:31.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Chakra is clearly visible\Nto the naked eye…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.65,0:08:34.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world is happening?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.94,0:08:37.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t tell me that\Nhe learned that Jutsu…!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.89,0:08:41.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is the Uchiha Clan…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.52,0:08:50.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.44,0:08:53.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What the heck is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.85,0:08:57.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a sound!\NWhat’s that technique?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.15,0:08:59.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s just a jab…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.89,0:09:00.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.06,0:09:05.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, it is the one used by\NLeaf Village’s number one technician.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.40,0:09:08.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s the only original technique\Nof the Copy Ninja, Kakashi…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.89,0:09:13.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s the special technique used\Nonly for assassinations…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.35,0:09:16.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Its secret is in the speed of the jab,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.89,0:09:19.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and also the physical aptitude\Nthat gives forth a gigantic Chakra,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.40,0:09:23.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the ability of the Chakra to\Nfocus solely on the target,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.48,0:09:27.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and moreover the speed of\Nthe jab makes a “chichichichichi” sound…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.44,0:09:31.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A unique sound attack similar\Nto the rumbling of a thousand birds.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.98,0:09:45.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that’s why that technique is called…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.77,0:09:52.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chidori: One Thousand Birds!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.94,0:10:32.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!\NThat Gaara’s absolute protection is…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.89,0:10:34.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s impossible…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.35,0:10:37.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t tell me…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.52,0:10:41.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excellent work…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.98,0:10:44.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.90,0:10:46.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kakashi’s…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.10,0:10:52.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chidori…\NAlso known as Lightning Blade.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.89,0:10:54.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lightning Blade?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.90,0:10:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lightning Blade is another name\Nfor the Jutsu derived
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.15,0:11:02.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,from Kakashi’s ability to cut through\Nlightning using that technique.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.35,0:11:05.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Cut through lightning?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.31,0:11:09.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? That sounds fishy…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.90,0:11:11.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Awesome…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.94,0:11:14.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The real name of that technique\Nis Chidori…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.73,0:11:20.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The secret is the speed of his jab\Nthat surpasses any human limitations
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.69,0:11:22.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the intensity of\Nthe Chakra on his arm…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.89,0:11:27.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that arm turns virtually\Ninto the equivalent of the swing
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.56,0:11:29.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,of a celebrated sword that\Ncuts through everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.89,0:11:34.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what a reckless technique…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.94,0:11:36.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s not for you to say…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.23,0:11:38.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Lee?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.89,0:11:43.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s beyond my scope of\Ncomprehension, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.73,0:11:45.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What an awesome technique!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.98,0:11:51.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can understand it…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.52,0:11:55.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it were me, if I made\Na running start at that speed,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.52,0:11:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn’t make a direct jab attack\Non the opponent…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.23,0:12:01.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or rather, I couldn’t.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.52,0:12:04.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For an opponent,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.98,0:12:07.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a straight line attack just gives him\Nan easy chance to launch a counterblow.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.60,0:12:13.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And moreover, I don’t have the eyes\Nto read that counterblow.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.35,0:12:19.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I envy you…Sasuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.85,0:12:24.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I fought you once, I said…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.89,0:12:27.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if one understands visually,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.35,0:12:29.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it’s meaningless unless\None can move physically…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.81,0:12:32.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was filled with\Na feeling of superiority.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.89,0:12:38.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But now, you have a body that moves\Nat the same high speed as mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.94,0:12:42.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Moreover, you have…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.60,0:12:45.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Sharingan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.35,0:12:48.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I caught you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.89,0:12:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Third Squadron.\NWe are ready any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.85,0:12:58.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All preparations are complete\Non this end too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.98,0:13:02.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger. Proceed with action\Nat the signal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.56,0:13:14.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like it’s almost time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.89,0:13:25.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The guy who was worrying about\NSasuke until just a moment ago…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.94,0:13:31.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is now jealous of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.31,0:13:37.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sasuke…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.65,0:13:41.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the feeling!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.27,0:13:46.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Summoning Jutsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.89,0:14:02.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ve gotten stronger…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.31,0:14:04.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to become Hokage…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.85,0:14:06.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order not to lose to anyone…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.15,0:14:09.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sasuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.44,0:14:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order not to lose to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.23,0:14:17.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want…to fight you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.89,0:14:20.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you are…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.81,0:14:23.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.31,0:14:46.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What…? This warm thing…?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.90,0:14:51.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother…? What is…?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.06,0:15:07.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blood…my blood is…!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.60,0:15:09.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don’t tell me that…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.35,0:15:25.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don’t tell me that\NGaara is hurt?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.89,0:15:35.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.65,0:15:37.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s that thing’s arm!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.02,0:15:48.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Darn! Doing something\Ncareless like that…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.89,0:15:55.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Has the Perfect Possession happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.98,0:15:59.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t know.\NHe seems to be injured…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.48,0:16:00.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This has never happened before.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.90,0:16:08.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It gives me the chills\Njust to remember…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.89,0:16:12.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I first saw that thing,\NI wasn’t able to eat…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.10,0:16:17.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, visually it’s totally…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.77,0:17:00.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.89,0:17:03.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,this sensation?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.19,0:17:43.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He’s hurt, after all…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.89,0:17:46.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The shell was broken when\Nhis body was incomplete!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.52,0:17:59.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s different! Those aren’t the eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.89,0:18:03.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What was that…\Nthat look earlier on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.81,0:18:45.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh…?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.23,0:19:02.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What’s this…? I can’t see…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.69,0:19:05.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kakashi! This must be!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.23,0:19:06.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah…a Genjutsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.81,0:19:09.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,– Release! 					– Release!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.77,0:19:25.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What’s going on…?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.89,0:19:27.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Release!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.73,0:19:32.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Genjutsu!\Nls Kabuto already moving?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.89,0:19:36.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, it’s just about time…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.65,0:19:42.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.56,0:20:17.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we begin?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.90,0:20:31.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s the signal!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.02,0:21:03.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,– Start the operation!\N– Start the operation!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.94,0:21:29.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone makes mistakes\Nlt’s nothing to be ashamed about
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.56,0:21:40.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t let this scar be for naught\NWalk with a smile
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.48,0:21:56.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, breathe in the air\NLift your face to the sky and jump
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.10,0:22:01.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it rains, take a break\NGo where the wind takes you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.60,0:22:06.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So many regrets\NDon’t let this scar be for naught
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.56,0:22:11.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s go carve the badges in our chest\NYes, it’s Show Time, life begins now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.81,0:22:21.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone makes mistakes\N It’s nothing to be ashamed about
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.15,0:22:32.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t let this scar be for naught\NWalk with a smile
