Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.31,0:22:48.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forge on strong
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.40,0:23:06.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It got dark all of a sudden…\Nit feels so good.
